ate your culture & replace you.\n\n(so maybe it's not such a bad Iran Deal, after all)", "author": "Lunar", "created": 1781743975214, "profile_picture": "AAVSlrgdPsSU", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "TenaciousDT", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Here's the UPSIDE of Trump's Iran Deal-- that Mark Levin, Ben Shapiro, Adam Schiff, and a SWARM of ZIOBOTS on PDW won't tell you: \ud835\ude4f\ud835\ude5d\ud835\ude5e\ud835\ude68 \ud835\ude3f\ud835\ude5a\ud835\ude56\ud835\ude61 \ud835\ude4e\ud835\ude3c\ud835\ude51\ud835\ude40\ud835\ude4e \ud835\ude48\ud835\ude3c\ud835\ude42\ud835\ude3c \ud835\ude41\ud835\ude67\ud835\ude64\ud835\ude62 \ud835\ude3d\ud835\ude5a\ud835\ude5e\ud835\ude63\ud835\ude5c \ud835\ude4e\ud835\ude4f\ud835\ude4a\ud835\ude48\ud835\ude4b\ud835\ude40\ud835\ude3f \ud835\ude5e\ud835\ude63 \ud835\ude69\ud835\ude5d\ud835\ude5a \ud835\ude48\ud835\ude44\ud835\ude3f\ud835\ude4f\ud835\ude40\ud835\ude4d\ud835\ude48\ud835\ude4e.  Uniparty Politicians & Israeli's don't care about that...", "last_comment_created": 1781766806901, "content": "<p>AIPAC is perfectly-happy to let the AIPAC Dems regain control of the Senate &amp; House.   And the White House in 2028.   It's all-the-same to them.  AIPAC RINOs are fine with being the Junior Partner in Business As Usual.</p>\n<p>It only harms MAGA and America.</p>\n<p>With Trump &amp; MAGA out of the way-- we can return the the Neocon Forever Wars of Bush Cheney McCain Hillary Obama LittleMarco Bolton Pelosi Cruz Haley McConnell Schumer Blinken Biden Kamala Zelenskyy.</p>\n<p>And no pesky antiwar protests when Dems are in charge of the wars.</p>\n<p>Of course, they'll have to censor your free speech, grab your guns, degenerate your culture &amp; replace yo